  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001467.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Ninĝirsu , Enlil's powerful warrior , Ur-Bau , ruler of Lagaš , the child born to Ninagala , built his E-ninnu-anzud-babbar , ( and ) built his E-dura ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001467.13",
      "line_range": "13",
      "translation": "(ii 5) For Bau , the kind woman , the child of An , he built her temple in Iri-kug ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001467.18",
      "line_range": "18",
      "translation": "(iii 1) For Ninkugnuna he built her temple in Urub ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001467.21",
      "line_range": "21",
      "translation": "(iii 4) For Enki , his master , he built his temple ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001467.25",
      "line_range": "25",
      "translation": "(iii 8) For Ninagala , his personal god , he built his temple ."
    }
  ],
